                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 25.) I took the prisoner in charge—I told him it was for uttering two forged orders on the 14th and 15th of Jan.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was driven to do this through distress.</p>
